    <h3>Quick Tips</h3>
    <ul class="quick-tips">
      <li>Practice your serve consistently - it's the only shot you have complete control over</li>
      <li>Return serves deep to keep opponents back</li>
      <li>Move forward after the third shot to gain net position</li>
      <li>Aim for your opponent's feet when they're transitioning</li>
      <li>Be patient at the kitchen line - don't pop up the ball</li>
      <li>Communicate with your partner about who takes which shots</li>
